{"tid":2159954,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應付壓力要聰明 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-08-16T15:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:53:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b5830ef840c794fe5bb558005de8f851f3b958","tid":2159954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200814/COBGYJGCHVGA5HDKQZPMOSRWLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200814%2FCOBGYJGCHVGA5HDKQZPMOSRWLM%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=e8345c8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200814%2FCOBGYJGCHVGA5HDKQZPMOSRWLM%2F&h=3fdd8967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200814/COBGYJGCHVGA5HDKQZPMOSRWLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n應付壓力要聰明 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qX9mpO_mnl2djtM1KLsyBzYnfOU=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6UPNPNR7EBFOPFNOHCGBHRTQ4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqX9mpO_mnl2djtM1KLsyBzYnfOU%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6UPNPNR7EBFOPFNOHCGBHRTQ4A.jpg&h=fcacf060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人的思想越複雜，。。。。。。。。。。。，不管發生什麼事都可以安然入睡。但都知道，那是一種福氣。<br />\n<br />\n我們嚮往生活無憂無慮，。。。。。。。。。。精明的人不但自己壓力大，你跟他交往，聽他事事周密，斤斤計較，即使不隨他一起做，也會傳染壓力，這便是我不願跟精明的人來往的原因，太累。<br />\n<br />\n交朋友，不要交精明的人，要交聰明人。精明和聰明雖一字之差，卻是天壤之別的兩種人。聰明人和精明人都會算，只是聰明人算長遠，精明人算眼前，格局不同，人生便不一樣。聰明人知道生活有壓力，但也知道「春有百花秋有月，夏有涼風冬有雪，若無閒事掛心頭，便是人間好時節。」如此便會得調劑會得到排遣，會自我減壓。這些，精明的人看不透想不穿，所以許多著名的精明人，笨起來則叫人目瞪口呆。可見精明能幹的日子，真的不如聰明伶俐。"}]}